  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Male or female suffering from mild hypertension (systolic BP between 130-165 mmHg,
             diastolic BP between 90-120 mmHg).

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Individuals with heart, kidney, thyroid disorders, diabetes, chronic disease or
             illness, neurological diseases, skin or bleeding disorders,

          -  Currently taking prescription or OTC medications and/or herb/supplements that effect
             BP or autonomic tone will not be recruited into the study.

          -  In addition, individuals who have a pacemaker and/or are pregnant will not be
             recruited in the study. A health history questionnaire was used to screen subjects.
      </textblock>
